snippet.title: Jack Frost (Nitrome.com) - Full Gameplay Levels 1-40
snippet.description:
Full gameplay of Jack Frost, one of the games of my childhood that I wanted to replay because it fits perfectly in winter and Christmas time.
I hope you like it!
